title: Gurney beats Greaves in deciding set at PDC Worlds
subtitle: Beau Greaves falls just short of becoming the second female player to win a match at the PDC World Championship, losing in the first round to 22nd seed Daryl Gurney.
full_text: Beau Greaves falls just short of becoming the second female player to win a match at the PDC World Championship, losing in the first round to 22nd seed Daryl Gurney.
